Renderer classes.

See: Description

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Viewport
    Stereo modes to be use by the 3D renderer.

Package org.morphus.renderer Description

Renderer classes. This packages contains abstract render class contains a very easy way to extend your own render from this one and be able to start rendering in 3d stereoscopic display without having to worry about much details of viewports and cameras.
